to do to try to help him sort

00:02:13.370 --> 00:02:17.300
of see this important
space one last time.

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:19.470
It was kind of a romantic idea.

00:02:19.470 --> 00:02:22.980
And I don't know, in
hindsight, how smart it was.

00:02:22.980 --> 00:02:25.250
In fact, it was a little dangerous.

00:02:25.250 --> 00:02:29.150
And lo and behold,
I - so I got lucky.

00:02:29.150 --> 00:02:32.920
I was one of the family members
who was chosen to go with him.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:37.380
And I went with my grandmother and
my grandfather and my Uncle Bob.

00:02:37.380 --> 00:02:38.920
And I met them over there.

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:42.140
