00:28:16.060 --> 00:28:17.360
&gt;&gt; Brendan Kiely: I would love it.

00:28:17.360 --> 00:28:22.120 position:56%
I would love it if there were a
movie of "The Last True Love Story."

00:28:22.120 --> 00:28:26.980
I have in my mind a kind of
